Class Leaser

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.wsact.mikand.pg4100.assignment1.LeasingManager.application.models.Leaser

  • public class Leaser
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Anders Mikkelsen on 27.01.15. This class defines a leaser object. The leaser object will service any customer that contacts it until stores close in the RentalProcessor.
